Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來戒指的束縛也撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些夜之愛子越來越脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是智世的使魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先回去她的影子裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 別發呆了 荊棘之子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡時間流逝比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暫時過來那一側吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且也不可能給人類醫生看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 我會離開一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前來這裡時 你拒絕進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次卻是我帶你進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半吊子難聞的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這麼火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的 最近來了個好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然比較古怪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在還不能起床
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我替你拆掉眼睛上的繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是妖精之國中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個叫蟻冢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 喝下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的身體滋生了太多魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血管和皮膚承受不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然暫時有那根魔繩抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的醫院明明也能做妥善的處置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精王真愛亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因為他想叫你們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是從小與人類的小孩交換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由人類撫養的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「調換兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎你來 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然還有臉來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}丘之防人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你養的孩子還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農把她帶走了 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩子有生命危險 當然要幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滿身都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們果然應該住在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女王 這可不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是我的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精們也會像人類或動物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因病或是年老而虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問艾利亞斯在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他在隨傳隨到的地方 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽說他是你的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們能夠互相溝通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一側的生物在很多問題上 與人類沒有共識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說是丈夫 更像魔法的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就當作是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏納罕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只過了三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說過 病人是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是夜之愛子 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是重傷患者 別隨便碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是啊 夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天我煮了月夜菇湯 你要早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉吵到你了 他是我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本是人類 和我調換在這邊長大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被調換後 我們都在對方的世界生活了半個世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半個世紀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}普通的人類要是一直待在這邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不再是人類 而會變成別的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的世界會毒害心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心中累積的毒素 總有一天會侵蝕身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算你沒事 智世也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那孩子更接近我們這邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你真為她著想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就應該讓她拋棄人類的身份 才更能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}否則 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定很快會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾經一直以為自己是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在人類世界的醫院工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卻被人類討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時 夏納罕過來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我現在才在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被人討厭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直不會衰老 就會讓人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對異類感到恐懼 是弱者的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做著我的工作 努力過好每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼好心虛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水池？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡的水有助於恢復傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少要先把表面的傷口治好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會刺痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像很冷 又好像很暖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以會無條件被夜之愛子吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我非常討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼吸…不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然還不太懂人類的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我想去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們總是偷偷可憐我 嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然人類會懼怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是接受我的 卻又總是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你可別低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要挺起胸膛 看好前方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望她 能夠以人類的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生靈的內心 也就是意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時候會成為無比強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要想活下去 你甚至能起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特別是在這邊的世界 這一點更加顯著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 就算流的血量足以致死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你卻沒有一絲想要活下去的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你的傷口才一直難以癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 你剛才抵抗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不管你多麼不想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要救活你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我希望你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷口癒合了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 我會離開一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快看 是報喪女妖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓她靜靜吧 多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憑依的家人不在了的傷心女人太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別待在這裡了 去別的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傾聽你聲音的家人已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說那邊的城鎮有很棒的男人在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報喪女妖在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還想…留在…他們的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那間房子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家人虔誠又奉守傳統 挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血脈總有斷絕的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但即便一個家崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要有人活著 就還有家的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要還有一個人活著 便會亮起燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不再有照亮你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次你去守護那個燈火便可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您好比一株銀色的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起消散於泡沫中 這樣更好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不必言謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護弱小 是我們守護者的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再會 報喪女妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 真的讓我很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道自己真的嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你還活著 我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬上要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩側的時間流逝不一樣 會有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好冷 腳要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍等 我去點暖爐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 家裡好像不太一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 不好意思回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到已經冬天了 我都有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回來了
Comment: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:33.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:47.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:04.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:10.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:23.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:29.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:35.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:42.03,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:50.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:33.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:47.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:57.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:04.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:10.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:23.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:29.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:35.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:42.03,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:50.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和魔法使共同度過的第一個聖誕節到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在年末倫敦的喧囂鬧市中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少女又見到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們今天去挑禮物吧

